{"tid":1794890,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【超高質】原創抗爭歌《星星之火》出咗MV啦！","createTime":"2019-12-23T12:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T12:34:01.000Z","uid":165773,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4ace802256f5e1230223cdc2234a66255a09f6","tid":1794890,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"FromJenna(vocal+MVproducer):<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jXd2cY_A2zA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjXd2cY_A2zA&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=82dc3281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jXd2cY_A2zA</a> <br />\n(English Subtitles Available)🔥結尾有我想對你們說的話，請看到最後‼️<br />\n.<br />\n因爲7月製作《香港人》(原曲：Shall We Talk) 而重新和 beats away 合作。當時他發給我這首歌的demo，我沒多想就答應參與了。<br />\n.<br />\n沒想到修改歌詞、錄音、混音、製作MV等等的工序，足足花了4個月多的時間🤦🏻&zwj;♀️ (我還特別為了這首歌去學唱歌😂⋯⋯)<br />\n.<br />\n一度以為這首歌要難產了🤦🏻&zwj;♀️幸好趕及在聖誕節前完成，希望能為大家打打氣！之後再跟你們細說裡面的故事吧❤️<br />\n.<br />\nPS. 特別鳴謝 ycpixels_ 願意把他在戰場上的影片給我製作MV🥺那些鏡頭真的很驚險😭😭💔<br />\n.<br />\nVocal by Jennachord<br />\nComposed and Produced by Beats Away<br />\nLyrics by Beats Away and Jennachord<br />\nVideo Recording by ycpixels_ (Instagram: ycpixels_)<br />\nVideo Editing by Jennachord"},{"pid":"1c904f45e16224dca5b8ed15d166ed011e68aa5e","tid":1794890,"uid":88940,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=34c180ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n唔好意思借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[行動] [推上熱門] 我宣佈 聽日平安夜攬炒正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid"